  <sect1 xml:id="virt.support.guests">
    <title>Supported VM Guests</title>
    <para>
   This section lists the support status for various guest operating systems
   virtualized on top of SUSE Linux Enterprise Server 12. All guest operating systems are supported
   both fully-virtualized and paravirtualized with two exceptions: Windows,
   which is only supported fully-virtualized, and OES and NetWare operating
   systems, which are only supported on Xen paravirtualized. All guest
   operating systems are supported both in 32-bit and 64-bit flavors, unless
   stated otherwise (see NetWare).
  </para>
